high_descs: Turn around and walk straight, then right to the corner vanity.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Turn left to the bath tub.
Place the sponge in the bath tub to the left of the drain.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed sponge in a bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a right at the shower and walk to the vanity table ahead.
Pick up the green sponge behind the box of tissues on top of the vanity counter.
Turn around, hang a left at the shower and turn right at the wall to reach the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around to face the white tub.
Put the rinsed sponge in the tub in front of the red towel.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed sponge in a tub.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter on your left.
Grab a sponge from the counter.
Walk to the left edge of the kitchen sink.
Place the sponge in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Turn around to the tub behind you.
Put the sponge in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Wet a sponge for use in a tub.
